@JaegerDemo.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7064

### Get Weather Forecast
GET {{JaegerDemo.Api_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast
Accept: application/json

### Get Weather for Specific City
GET {{JaegerDemo.Api_HostAddress}}/weather/London
Accept: application/json

### Get Weather for Another City
GET {{JaegerDemo.Api_HostAddress}}/weather/Tokyo
Accept: application/json

### Bulk Weather Processing
POST {{JaegerDemo.Api_HostAddress}}/weather/bulk
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cities": ["New York", "London", "Tokyo", "Sydney", "Paris"]
}

###

